metadata.name: Clarence with Waffle Pop & Black Forest Cake
metadata.description: Clarence with the Waffle Pop is a cheeky ape, absolutely delighted with his scrumptious chocolate banana waffle pop and black forest cherry cake. Clarence is one of three apes in our flagship collection with two desserts. That toothy smile and happy demeanor will lure you in. 1 of 1 hand-drawn art by award-winning NFT artist J.J. Weinberg, based in Chicago, US.
